enough for bringing him back.

25:13.137 --> 25:14.827
- Well, we all got him back.

25:16.551 --> 25:18.551
- Kayce used to tell me
what a war it was for you,

25:18.620 --> 25:19.931
keeping this place.

25:21.448 --> 25:23.068
