26:57.482 --> 27:00.275
- All right, coming shotgun
there, huh?

27:11.896 --> 27:15.172
- Stick that horse
back in the barn.

27:15.241 --> 27:18.068
Move your gear
out of the bunkhouse.

27:18.137 --> 27:19.103
- Move it where?

27:19.172 --> 27:20.758
- The lodge.

27:26.931 --> 27:29.034
- Why?

27:29.103 --> 27:30.724
- 'Cause I can't have
the Livestock Commissioner

27:30.793 --> 27:33.482
